The number of salespeople required at a 24-hour convenience store in different time periods is as follows: 2:00-6:00 - 10 people, 6:00-10:00 - 15 people, 10:00-14:00 - 25 people, 14:00-18:00 - 20 people, 18:00-22:00 - 18 people, 22:00-2:00 - 12 people. Salespeople start their shifts at 2:00, 6:00, 10:00, 14:00, 18:00, and 22:00, working continuously for 8 hours. Determine the minimum number of salespeople needed to meet the requirements.
-------------
【Python Gurobi 代码】:
 ```python
from gurobipy import Model, GRB

# Create model
model = Model("Convenience_Store_Staffing")

# Decision variables
# x1: start at 2:00
# x2: start at 6:00
# x3: start at 10:00
# x4: start at 14:00
# x5: start at 18:00
# x6: start at 22:00
x1 = model.addVar(vtype=GRB.INTEGER, name="x1")
x2 = model.addVar(vtype=GRB.INTEGER, name="x2")
x3 = model.addVar(vtype=GRB.INTEGER, name="x3")
x4 = model.addVar(vtype=GRB.INTEGER, name="x4")
x5 = model.addVar(vtype=GRB.INTEGER, name="x5")
x6 = model.addVar(vtype=GRB.INTEGER, name="x6")

# Objective: minimize total number of salespeople
model.setObjective(x1 + x2 + x3 + x4 + x5 + x6, GRB.MINIMIZE)

# Constraints for each time period
# 2:00-6:00 (covered by x1 and x6)
model.addConstr(x1 + x6 >= 10, name="c1")

# 6:00-10:00 (covered by x1 and x2)
model.addConstr(x1 + x2 >= 15, name="c2")

# 10:00-14:00 (covered by x2 and x3)
model.addConstr(x2 + x3 >= 25, name="c3")

# 14:00-18:00 (covered by x3 and x4)
model.addConstr(x3 + x4 >= 20, name="c4")

# 18:00-22:00 (covered by x4 and x5)
model.addConstr(x4 + x5 >= 18, name="c5")

# 22:00-2:00 (covered by x5 and x6)
model.addConstr(x5 + x6 >= 12, name="c6")

# Optimize
model.optimize()

# Output results
if model.status == GRB.OPTIMAL:
    print("Minimum number of salespeople needed:", int(model.objVal))
    print("Number starting at 2:00:", int(x1.x))
    print("Number starting at 6:00:", int(x2.x))
    print("Number starting at 10:00:", int(x3.x))
    print("Number starting at 14:00:", int(x4.x))
    print("Number starting at 18:00:", int(x5.x))
    print("Number starting at 22:00:", int(x6.x))
```
