Consider assigning $n=2$ factories to $n$ locations. The transportation volume between factory $i$ and factory $j$ is $d_{ij}$, and the unit transportation cost from location $p$ to location $q$ is $c_{pq}$. The specific values are shown in the following table: Table 1.1

|        | Transportation volume to Location 1 | Transportation volume to Location 2 | Transportation cost to Location 1 | Transportation cost to Location 2 |
| :----: | :---------------------------------: | :---------------------------------: | :-------------------------------: | :-------------------------------: |
| Factory 1 | 10 | 20 | 5 | 8 |
| Factory 2 | 30 | 40 | 6 | 7 |

In order to minimize the total transportation cost, formulate this problem as an integer model.
-------------
【Python Gurobi 代码】:
 ```python
import gurobipy as gp
from gurobipy import GRB

# Data
n = 2

# Transportation volume between factories (d_ij)
d = [
    [10, 20],
    [30, 40]
]

# Unit transportation cost between locations (c_pq)
c = [
    [5, 8],
    [6, 7]
]

# Create model
model = gp.Model("Quadratic_Assignment_Problem")

# Decision variables: x[i,p] = 1 if factory i is assigned to location p
x = model.addVars(n, n, vtype=GRB.BINARY, name="x")

# Objective function: minimize total transportation cost
model.setObjective(
    gp.quicksum(d[i][j] * c[p][q] * x[i, p] * x[j, q]
                for i in range(n)
                for j in range(n)
                for p in range(n)
                for q in range(n)),
    GRB.MINIMIZE
)

# Constraints:
# Each factory is assigned to exactly one location
for i in range(n):
    model.addConstr(gp.quicksum(x[i, p] for p in range(n)) == 1, name=f"Factory_{i}")

# Each location has exactly one factory
for p in range(n):
    model.addConstr(gp.quicksum(x[i, p] for i in range(n)) == 1, name=f"Location_{p}")

# Optimize
model.optimize()

# Output results
if model.status == GRB.OPTIMAL:
    print(f"Optimal objective value: {model.objVal}")
    for i in range(n):
        for p in range(n):
            if x[i, p].x > 0.5:
                print(f"Factory {i+1} is assigned to Location {p+1}")
```
